{"tid":1982474,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「由華為手機拍攝」再遭揭發造假，官方比賽宣傳片影像原來是用 Nikon D850 拍攝的","createTime":"2020-04-21T08:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:34:47.000Z","uid":1121,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9ece2a37a807f48a7bed59731c6b82d9571ec04b","tid":1982474,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"企業開辦的攝影比賽宣傳物資多會以主辦公司器材拍攝，華為攝影比賽「2020 華為新影像大赛」一段宣傳影片以不同照片組成，該片段結尾標有「由華為手機拍攝」字樣，卻被眼利網民發現部分照片實由 Nikon 單反相機拍攝，事件被揭發後官方在微博發表道歉聲明，並刪除有關字句。<br />\n<br />\n揭發事件的網民 @Jamie-hua 為蘋果 2018 年 iPhone 攝影比賽（iPhone Photography Awards）亞軍，他 4 月 17 日中午在微博撰文指華為攝影比賽的宣傳影片中，有數張風景照甚為眼熟，翻查之下發現該些照片的 Exif 信息顯示著拍攝工具為 Nikon D850 單反相機，其他照片也有眼熟之處，但因為不太記得清於是作罷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/1-25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F1-25.jpg&h=c02b8173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片由攝影師 Su Tie 以 Nikon D850 拍攝。（出自 500px）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F6-12.jpg&h=da58a12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/7-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F7-10.jpg&h=59f37991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/8-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F8-9.jpg&h=1ae03f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/10-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F10-6.jpg&h=ef8d0168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/9-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F9-7.jpg&h=e0a84677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為同日晚上在官方微博發出致歉聲明，指出該段影片收納了 30 多幅從不同攝影師而來的作品，但因「小編工作疏忽」，在影片結尾「錯誤地標註」照片由華為手機拍攝，表示已刪除有關字句，並感謝網友指出錯處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2-21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F2-21.jpg&h=dd83e988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為在手機行業中且算頗有名氣的品牌，尤其「手機攝影師」愛戴，但造假並非首次。其網上宣傳物資都應該經由嚴密審批方能登出， 這個「疏忽」是否只由小編造成，大家又怎樣看呢？"},{"pid":"cadb9df9f7bc35068c1d1a83abfeb19da7dd1119","tid":1982474,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/266835/「由華為手機拍攝」再遭揭發造假，官方比賽宣傳/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F266835%2F%E3%80%8C%E7%94%B1%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E3%80%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%2F&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=112c7eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/266835/「由華為手機拍攝」再遭揭發造假，官方比賽宣傳/</a>"},{"pid":"829ef01be67cf75dab47f928d53fde737f3598cc","tid":1982474,"uid":255744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經知道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd565edf292fb3c76de91d2e2a7c60c8d9f00b1","tid":1982474,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"影下月亮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8763adc96594376429130f9a6845aa2eb1273991","tid":1982474,"uid":22701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"年年都玩做假, cls 